ORF515 | Asset Pricing II: Stoch Calc Adv Deriv | http://www.blackboard.princeton.edu | instructors:Birgit Rudloff description:Course covers the pricing and hedging of advanced derivatives, including topics such as exotic options, greeks, interest rate derivatives and credit derivatives, as well as covering the basics of stochastic calculus necessary for finance.  Designed for Masters students.
